msgid ""
"Once you click \"Yes, end my proctored exam\", the exam will be closed, and "
"your proctoring session will be submitted for review."
msgstr ""
"Po kliknięciu \"Tak, zakończ mój egzamin z nadzorem\", egzamin zostanie "
